response.overview: 「ONEW Japan 1st Concert Tour 2022 ～Life goes on～」 was the first concert tour by ONEW. It was in support of his debut Japanese album Life Goes On (2022). The tour took place from July 8 to September 11, 2022 with eight shows in four prefectures across Japan. The recording for this release took place on September 11 at Yoyogi National Stadium in Tokyo.
response.title: 「ONEW Japan 1st Concert Tour 2022 ～Life goes on～」
